{
  "stem": "7160.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sometimes we used to see trespassing, we used to give them such a beating when he never could put his foot there to protect the people inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was about 500 people in the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I did job to us-- I was up besides-- because not always I used to go-- I used to go for the trips, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes I used to stay two, three weeks, you know, stay home to see if everything is OK.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To watch around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How many guards is watching the borders and blah, blah, blah, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We have to be prepared before you make a such a decision, because was too many lives involved in it, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They can get hurt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They get in big trouble, including me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Probably they send me to Siberia or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, we were crossing the borders, and the Russians don't play games.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very strict in those things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So and that's why I was a policeman there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Watching over the people in the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Me and a few other more people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, actually, that was my home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was there from 19-- mid 1945 till 1949-- '48, but from there I had to skip and went to Germany because I was afraid they was going to catch me when I escaped from the prison.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I lived in Germany for awhile in disguise.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I come with my wife's name into the United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we come here I had a child, was six months old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- you want to hear a little thing of what happened in the ship?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when I went on the ship-- the ship's name was Was a soldiers ship.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
